\c 142 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 142\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Kadhata Nama Ari'atamaa (Mararoo Daawit, isa yeroo inni holqa keessa ture; kadhata)
\m \bd 1\bd* Ani sagalee koo ol fuudhee gara Waaqayyootti nan iyyadha, Waaqayyo akka anatti araaramuuf sagalee kootiin nan kadhadha.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ani dhibee koo isa duratti nan dhangalaasa, rakkina koos isa duratti nan himadha!
\m \bd 3\bd* Hafuurri koo yeroo ana keessatti laafu, ati gara ani itti adeemu in beekta! Daandii ani irra adeemu keessa, isaan futtaasaa anaaf dhoksaniiru.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ani gara mirga koo nan ilaala, nan eegas; garuu namni na yaadatu hin jiru; iddoon ani kooluu itti galu tokko illee anaaf hin hafne; namni tokko illee dhimma koo hin qabu!
\m \bd 5\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ani gara keetti nan iyyadha, "Ati isa ani kooluu itti galuu dha, biyya warra jiraatoo keessattis qooda koo ti" nan jedha.
\m \bd 6\bd* Ani baay'isee waanan mataa buuseef, iyyata koo anaaf dhaggeeffadhu! Warri na ari'atan baay'ee waan anatti cimaniif, ati isaan jalaa na baafadhu!
\m \bd 7\bd* Maqaa kee akkan galateeffadhutti, mana hidhaa keessaa na baasi! Yeroo ati waan gaarii anaaf deebiftettis, warri qajeelonni anatti in tuuta'u.
